### OrgUnit 4: Customer Operations
POST {{baseUrl}}/oslc/solartech/resources
Content-Type: text/turtle
Slug: org-customer-ops

@prefix dcterms: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> .
@prefix rdf:     <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> .
@prefix bmm:     <http://www.omg.org/spec/BMM#> .

<> a bmm:OrganizationUnit ;
   dcterms:title "Customer Operations" ;
   dcterms:description "Sales, installation coordination, warranty service, and the certified installer network. Responsible for the customer satisfaction goal and customer experience strategy." .

### ── Business Processes ──────────────────────────────────────────────

### Process 1: Product Development Lifecycle
POST {{baseUrl}}/oslc/solartech/resources
Content-Type: text/turtle
Slug: process-product-dev

@prefix dcterms: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> .
@prefix rdf:     <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> .
@prefix bmm:     <http://www.omg.org/spec/BMM#> .

<> a bmm:BusinessProcess ;
   dcterms:title "Product Development Lifecycle" ;
   dcterms:description "End-to-end process from research concept through prototype, certification testing (IEC 61215/61730), manufacturing transfer, and product launch. Governed by the Product Quality Standards policy." .

### Process 2: Order-to-Installation
POST {{baseUrl}}/oslc/solartech/resources
Content-Type: text/turtle
Slug: process-order-install

@prefix dcterms: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> .
@prefix rdf:     <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> .
@prefix bmm:     <http://www.omg.org/spec/BMM#> .

<> a bmm:BusinessProcess ;
   dcterms:title "Order-to-Installation" ;
   dcterms:description "Customer inquiry, site assessment, system design, permitting, installation, inspection, and grid connection. Governed by the warranty response time and installer certification rules." .

### Process 3: Warranty Service
POST {{baseUrl}}/oslc/solartech/resources
Content-Type: text/turtle
Slug: process-warranty

@prefix dcterms: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> .
@prefix rdf:     <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> .
@prefix bmm:     <http://www.omg.org/spec/BMM#> .

<> a bmm:BusinessProcess ;
   dcterms:title "Warranty Claim Resolution" ;
   dcterms:description "Receive claim, triage severity, dispatch technician, diagnose issue, repair or replace, close claim. Must comply with the 48-hour response time business rule." .

### ── Assets ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Asset 1: Manufacturing Facility
POST {{baseUrl}}/oslc/solartech/resources
Content-Type: text/turtle
Slug: asset-mfg-facility

@prefix dcterms: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> .
@prefix rdf:     <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> .
@prefix bmm:     <http://www.omg.org/spec/BMM#> .

<> a bmm:Asset ;
   dcterms:title "Austin Manufacturing Campus" ;
   dcterms:description "500MW annual capacity solar panel manufacturing facility in Austin, TX. Includes cell fabrication, module assembly, and electroluminescence testing lines." .

### Asset 2: Patent Portfolio
POST {{baseUrl}}/oslc/solartech/resources
Content-Type: text/turtle
Slug: asset-patents

@prefix dcterms: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> .
@prefix rdf:     <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> .
@prefix bmm:     <http://www.omg.org/spec/BMM#> .

<> a bmm:Asset ;
   dcterms:title "Perovskite Tandem Cell Patent Portfolio" ;
   dcterms:description "12 granted patents and 8 pending applications covering perovskite-silicon tandem cell architecture, encapsulation methods, and manufacturing processes." .

### Asset 3: Monitoring Platform
POST {{baseUrl}}/oslc/solartech/resources
Content-Type: text/turtle
Slug: asset-monitoring-platform

@prefix dcterms: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> .
@prefix rdf:     <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> .
@prefix bmm:     <http://www.omg.org/spec/BMM#> .

<> a bmm:Asset ;
   dcterms:title "SolarWatch Monitoring Platform" ;
   dcterms:description "Cloud-based IoT platform monitoring 85,000 installed systems in real-time. Provides energy production analytics, fault detection, and proactive warranty alerts." .
